<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n12027f"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n12" href="#n12027f">N12 (VI.B.14)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n12all.htm#n12027f"> 27(f)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Hush, when you give, / Tell, when you sell</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Soyez muet, quand vous donnez; / Quand on vous donne, parlez. <br><font color="green">[Be silent when you give, speak when you receive.]</font> <small> L-F. Sauv&eacute, <a name="LFSP" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#LFSP"><cite title="source">Proverbes et dictons de la Basse-Bretagne</cite></a> (1878) 55</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
